refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;
timezoneId
The timezone identifier, like UTC, Africa/Lagos, Asia/Hong_Kong, or Europe/Lisbon. The list of valid identifiers is available in the .

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 This function returns &false; if the
 timezoneId isn't valid, or &true;
 otherwise.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Getting the default timezone


<?php
date_default_timezone_set('America/Los_Angeles');

$script_tz = date_default_timezone_get();

if (strcmp($script_tz, ini_get('date.timezone'))){
    echo 'Script timezone differs from ini-set timezone.';
} else {
    echo 'Script timezone and ini-set timezone match.';
}
?>
